thread.title: Two taken to hospital after suspect package at parliament

title: Two taken to hospital after suspect package at parliament
text: March 12, 2018 / 2:59 PM / Updated 21 minutes ago Two taken to hospital after suspect package at parliament Reuters Staff 1 Min Read LONDON (Reuters) - Two people were taken to hospital as a precaution, as detectives investigated a suspect package at Britain’s parliament, police said in a statement on Monday. “Specialist officers are in attendance and the package is being assessed,” the statement said. “London Ambulance Service attended and two people, a man and a woman, have been taken to hospital as a precaution.” Reporting by William James; writing by Alistair Smout; editing by Stephen Addison
